                     <hi rend="smallCaps">GUILTY</hi> 
                     <hi rend="italic">of Burglary</hi>. Aged 20.—<hi rend="italic">Recommended to mercy by the Prosecutor.</hi>
                  </rs>—
<rs id="t18511215-131-punishment-51" type="punishmentDescription">
