                  </rs>.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="largeCaps">HAMILTON</hi>—
<rs id="t18511215-131-verdict-3" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18511215-131-verdict-3" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
