                     <hi rend="smallCaps">GUILTY</hi> 
                     <hi rend="italic">of Receiving</hi>. Aged 29.—<hi rend="italic">Strongly recommended to mercy by the Jury and Prosecutor.</hi>
                  </rs>—
<rs id="t18511215-131-punishment-52" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18511215-131-punishment-52" type="punishmentCategory" value="imprison"></interp>
